# My Life App — Cursor AI Rules

## What This App Is
My Life is a productivity and life management mobile app designed to help users Thrive. It promotes organization, personal growth, and life balance by centralizing all aspects of a user's life into one intelligent platform. The app is built around a visual "Life Wheel" concept where users organize everything — tasks, goals, habits, events, and people — under customizable life categories called Life Areas.

