## Database Schema Summary

| Table | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `profiles` | User profiles extending Supabase auth |
| `life_bubbles` | Life Areas |
| `tasks` | All Entry types |
| `events` | Calendar events with recurrence |
| `habits` | Habit definitions |
| `occurrences` | Habit and task completion tracking |
| `people` | Contacts and relationships |
| `recycle_bin` | Soft-deleted items |
| `notifications` | In-app notification system |
| `bubble_shares` | Active Life Area sharing |
| `pending_shares` | Pending invites for non-users |

### Key RPC Functions
- `activate_pending_invite(invite_code)` — Activates a Life Area share
- `lookup_user_by_email(email)` — Finds user by email for linking
- `notify_linked_user(...)` — Sends in-app notification
- `respond_to_connection(person_id, responder_user_id, status)` — Approves/declines connection

